## Calculate Converted Amount [/USD/to/GBP]

### Calculate Converted Amount GBP [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "base": "USD",
            "target_currency": "GBP",
            "amount": 500
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "success": true,
            "base": "USD",
            "target_currency": "GBP",
            "amount": 500,
            "exchange_rate": 0.832,
            "converted_amount": 416
        }
        
