# Add New Currency [/currencies]

## Add Currency Exchange Rate [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "currency": "AUD",
            "exchange_rate": 1.410
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "currency": "AUD",
            "exchange_rate": 1.410
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type1: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "Invalid parameters. Please specify 'currency' and 'exchange_rate' parameters."
            }

+ Response 409 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type2: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "The currency you requested already exists."
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type3: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "An error occurred while processing your request."
            }
    
        
## Update-Delete Currency Rate [/currencies/{currency}]

### Update Currency Exchange Rate [PUT]

+ Parameters

    + currency (string, required) - รหัสสกุลเงินที่ต้องการอัปเดต เช่น GBP, EUR, JPY เป็นต้น

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "currency": "GBP",
            "exchange_rate": 0.9
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "currency": "GBP",
            "exchange_rate": 0.9
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type1: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "Invalid parameters. Please specify 'currency' and 'exchange_rate' parameters."
            }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type2: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "The currency you requested does not exist or is not supported."
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Content-Type3: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "error": "An error occurred while processing your request."
            }

### Delete Currency [DELETE]

+ Parameters

    + currency (string, required) - รหัสสกุลเงินที่ต้องการลบ เช่น GBP, EUR, JPY เป็นต้น

+ Response 204





